{"tid":2034832,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"黃金加速外流，支幣變廢紙？4月有10.3噸黃金從中國流出至香港，史上首次！","createTime":"2020-05-25T13:07:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-26T05:36:03.000Z","uid":48040,"like":19,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"8f304408f955fd28c2408e767c4a153d33710cfd","tid":2034832,"uid":48040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T13:07:25.000Z","msg":"現代貨幣其實就是一張紙，假如一個國家的美元儲備不足或者黃金儲備不足，咁遇上經濟動盪的時候，貨幣就有可能變成廢紙。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://cn.reuters.com/article/china-hk-gold-trade-0525-idCNKBS2310Y5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcn.reuters.com%2Farticle%2Fchina-hk-gold-trade-0525-idCNKBS2310Y5&d=g30fgRh1OaLpBbOto8aU3hjE8xiivR5AeW87zNloLfY%3D&h=39062018\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcn.reuters.com%2Farticle%2Fchina-hk-gold-trade-0525-idCNKBS2310Y5&h=9458ce35\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://cn.reuters.com/article/china-hk-gold-trade-0525-idCNKBS2310Y5</a><br />\n<br />\n香港政府統計處週一公佈的4月份黃金貿易數據顯示，<span style=\"color: gold;\">4月罕有出現由中國內地淨取代黃金至香港，淨換算黃金量為10,300公斤；為路透自2012年追踪有關數據以來，首次錄得由內地淨流出。</span><br />\n據統計處電子郵件給路透的最新數據，4月香港對內地的黃金總出口（本地出口及轉口）為4,213公斤（4.213噸），按月大減逾七成；自身自內地進口的黃金量14,513公斤，<span style=\"color: gold;\">月內由內地淨達到至10,300公斤</span>，3月由香港淨流入內地則為13,523公斤。今年首四個月，香港淨流入內地黃金量為17,132公斤，減少89％。<br />\n（其實上述數字只包括合法途徑，實際上2019年時候海關就曾破獲黃金走私案件。2020年有幾多黃金走私，就唔知啦。）<br />\n<br />\n=====<br />\n五毛睇死呢個channel的follower唔會過一萬。你可以幫幫手嗎？<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/_OtH-ee5lSw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F_OtH-ee5lSw&d=g30fgRh1OaLpBbOto8aU3hjE8xiivR5AeW87zNloLfY%3D&h=9b3bf830\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/_OtH-ee5lSw</a>"},{"pid":"ec5dd507fc86ec5c6e5eeab3ec0b836002821faf","tid":2034832,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T13:10:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"488514ae3a80e0bdafbcd652fb9e4f9c1300fcca","tid":2034832,"uid":48040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ec5dd507fc86ec5c6e5eeab3ec0b836002821faf","tid":2034832,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T13:10:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T13:11:12.000Z","msg":"黃金gogogo"},{"pid":"03d982035214564f9e500edc977e68bafc2296fa","tid":2034832,"uid":48040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T13:14:29.000Z","msg":"輕輕一推 必有迴響"},{"pid":"bf0ec2535839ba37e9a4de7f1b63052f5601d312","tid":2034832,"uid":268942,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T13:15:07.000Z","msg":"中國的黃金?據說會生鏽。"},{"pid":"89910a79dd13455508639b3ca8f49d60efe4ee51","tid":2034832,"uid":48040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bf0ec2535839ba37e9a4de7f1b63052f5601d312","tid":2034832,"uid":268942,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T13:15:07.000Z","msg":"中國的黃金?據說會生鏽。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T13:15:55.000Z","msg":"會甩色"},{"pid":"85a7cd0c07bce5e9d5f4c823f273a9def2fcfe5d","tid":2034832,"uid":98431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T13:16:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbad78e7002922f9fb6ea7eac0dcb82702377903","tid":2034832,"uid":327740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T13:16:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"35fa9931d57124bea24b033b1bca726d30c1e0f7","tid":2034832,"uid":108337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T13:18:21.000Z","msg":"走私黃金"},{"pid":"20d38411f2b4425c5d98ed20f7ce0d66cea6058c","tid":2034832,"uid":294518,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime